$ Perl module ExtUtils::MakeMaker
@ ExtUtils::MakeMaker

code {
use ExtUtils::MakeMaker;

WriteMakefile(
    NAME            => 'Foo::Bar::Baz.pm',
    VERSION_FROM    => 'lib/Foo/Bar/Baz.pm'
);
code }


Apparently, `Module::Build` is an alternative to `ExtUtils::MakeMaker`.

